channel.title: Omg?
channel.description:
Hi Moparscape,
This is really bs. My school got swine flu. So like 2 days ago they said that school will open tomorrow. Now they sent my mom an email saying school will close till Sunday. Seriously... School must get their facts straight. My parents already ironed my clothes :|
